1. Oni su *gej* par. (They are a gay couple.)
2. Ona svoj život posvećuje pravima *gej* osoba. (She is devoted to advocating for the rights of gay people.)
3. *Gej* komunikacija se razvija na sve većem nivou. (Gay communication is developing at an increasing level.)
4. Ona je otvoreno priznala da je *gej*. (She openly admitted that she is gay.)
5. U većem broju država je legalizovan *gej* brak. (In a larger number of countries, gay marriage is legalized.)